Package src.Map

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Map
    Stores all details about the map, including what tile is in each position and randomises the tile placement each time a new map gets generated.
    MapSegment
    Stores the tile IDs of the tiles in the map tile segment.
    MapSegmentHandler
    Loads all map segments given the formats provided by the text file
    PathFindingGrid
    This represents the grid of directions for characters to move to find the player character
    PFNode
    The Path finding grid consists of Path Finding Nodes that store distance to the player and the direction to move to get to the player as quickly as possible
